snippet.title: news.com.au
snippet.description:
The official YouTube channel of Australia's number one news site news.com.au. 

News.com.au delivers the news in colour spanning entertainment, travel, lifestyle, sport, business, technology, money and real estate. We live to engage with our viewers and at appropriate times provide an alternate angle on the news that involves humour when least expected. 

Our video content aims to be entertaining, fresh and giving a unique and colourful take on news in Australia, around the world and across the Internet.
